---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Expense Tracker Privacy Policy - Logicpath Systems">
    <section class="legal-page" style="padding-top: 120px; min-height: 100vh;">
        <div class="container reveal">
            <div class="glass-card" style="padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);">
                <header style="margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: center;">
                    <h1 class="gradient-text">Privacy Policy</h1>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary);"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> March 21, 2026</p>
                </header>

                <main class="legal-content">
                    <p>This privacy policy applies to the <strong>Expense Tracker</strong> app (hereby referred to as "Application") for mobile devices that was created by Logicpath Systems (hereby referred to as "Service Provider") as a free service. This service is intended for use "AS IS".</p>

                    <h2>1. Data Collection and Use</h2>
                    <p>The Application is designed with a strict "local-first" and offline-only approach. <strong>The Service Provider does not collect, transmit, store, or have access to any of your personal or financial data.</strong></p>
                    <p>All information you provide—including transactions, categories, amounts, and notes—is saved exceptionally on your device's local storage. The Application does not communicate with any external servers or databases to store your information.</p>

                    <h2>2. Local Storage and Data Retention</h2>
                    <p>Because your data is stored locally on your device:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>You have complete control over your data.</li>
                        <li><strong>If you uninstall the Application, clear the Application's data from your device settings, or lose your device, your data will be permanently deleted.</strong></li>
                        <li>The Service Provider cannot recover lost data under any circumstances.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>3. Backups</h2>
                    <p>The Application provides functionalities to export your data (e.g., as a JSON backup or CSV export). When you use these features, the data is generated locally on your device. It is your sole responsibility to securely store and manage these backup files. The Service Provider has no access to your backups.</p>

                    <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
                    <p>The Application does not integrate with third-party analytics, crash reporting, or advertising services that track your behavior or collect your personal information.</p>

                    <h2>5. Security</h2>
                    <p>The Service Provider values your trust in using the Application. All your data remains localized within the secure sandbox provided by your device's operating system. However, please be aware that no method of electronic storage on a mobile device is 100% secure, and the Service Provider cannot guarantee its absolute security. It is recommended that you secure your device using standard screen locks (PIN, password, biometric) to prevent unauthorized access to your local data.</p>

                    <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
                    <p>The Application does not address anyone under the age of 13. The Service Provider does not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13 years of age.</p>

                    <h2>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <p>The Service Provider may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. The Service Provider will notify you of any changes by updating the "Effective Date" at the top of this Privacy Policy.</p>

                    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>If you have any questions or suggestions about this Privacy Policy, please feel free to reach out to us at:</p>
                    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@logicpathsystems.com" style="color: var(--accent-secondary);">contact@logicpathsystems.com</a></p>
                </main>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .legal-content h2 {
        color: var(--text-primary);
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .legal-content p, .legal-content ul {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .legal-content ul {
        padding-left: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .legal-content li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
</style>
